# Walkthrough: Hierarchical Agent + Chainlit + HITL

## Architecture

```mermaid
graph TD
    A[User Message] --> B[🎯 Supervisor]
    B --> C[📋 Specialist]
    C --> D[📝 Planner]
    D --> E[⚡ Executor]
    E --> F{🛡️ HITL Approval}
    F -->|Approve| G[🔧 Execute Tool]
    F -->|Reject| H[⏭️ Skip]
    G --> I[🧐 Validator]
    H --> I
    I -->|NEXT_STEP| E
    I -->|RETRY| E
    I -->|REPLAN| D
    I -->|FINISH| J[💬 Responsor]
    J --> K[Final Answer]
```

## HITL in Action

Before executing any tool, the agent pauses and shows **Approve/Reject** buttons:

![HITL Approval Dialog](file:///Users/tai.pham/.gemini/antigravity/brain/a6ae8710-4789-427d-9cf3-7c47ed57935f/hitl_screenshot.png)

![HITL Demo Recording](file:///Users/tai.pham/.gemini/antigravity/brain/a6ae8710-4789-427d-9cf3-7c47ed57935f/hitl_demo.webp)

## How to Run

```bash
cd apps/agent-service
uv run chainlit run chainlit_app.py -w --port 8001
```

Then open **http://localhost:8001** in your browser.

## Key Files

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| [chainlit_app.py](file:///Users/tai.pham/Project/planning_agent/apps/agent-service/chainlit_app.py) | Chainlit UI with HITL |
| [hierarchical_graph.py](file:///Users/tai.pham/Project/planning_agent/apps/agent-service/app/agents/workflows/hierarchical_graph.py) | Core agent graph |
| [routes.py](file:///Users/tai.pham/Project/planning_agent/apps/agent-service/app/api/routes.py) | REST API (V4) |
